re doing, and more importantly why.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"attachment wp-att-5317\" href=\"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/2011\/01\/good-to-great\/photo-2\/\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-5317\" title=\"progress board\" src=\"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2011\/01\/photo-2-1024x764.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"614\" height=\"458\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We all make resolutions for the new year &#8211; lose weight, connect with old friends, train for that half-marathon. What about being the best at &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[16],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5314"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5314"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5314\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5314"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5314"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5314"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}